Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}吹け吹け　叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}可那风儿 越吼越凶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}わたしは　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}但我依然 梦想在胸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}しゃぼん玉　信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}肥皂泡中 定有彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:46.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}予期せぬ　上昇して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:46.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}偶尔得志 腾云行空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}嵐に　下降して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}偶尔迷失 风暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:54.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}あらがう　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:54.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}抗争不止 信念不松
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}しゃぼん玉　生きてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}肥皂泡儿 亦能腾空
